        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Modernizing the Veterans On-Campus Experience Act of 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill removes the requirement that educational and vocational counseling services provided by the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) on&amp;nbsp;campus at institutions of higher learning must be provided by VA counselors.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
